Also takes note with appreciation of the Lima Declaration of Guidelines on Auditing Precepts of 1977
Adopted by the Ninth Congress of the International Organization of Supreme Audit Institutions, Lima, 17–26 October 1977. and the Mexico Declaration on Supreme Audit Institutions Independence of 2007,
Adopted by the Nineteenth Congress of the International Organization of Supreme Audit Institutions, Mexico City, 5–10 November 2007. and encourages Member States to apply, in a manner consistent with their national institutional structures, the principles set out in those Declarations;
